  "content": "<p data-pid=\"D463Yy_m\">首先，题主贴的这个图：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-76cc2766f4418e88125a1735cbe31ff4_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"662\" data-rawheight=\"437\" data-original-token=\"v2-76cc2766f4418e88125a1735cbe31ff4\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-96e193d29c39a0479adee80f5fb724bb_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"662\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-76cc2766f4418e88125a1735cbe31ff4_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;662&#39; height=&#39;437&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"662\" data-rawheight=\"437\" data-original-token=\"v2-76cc2766f4418e88125a1735cbe31ff4\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-96e193d29c39a0479adee80f5fb724bb_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"662\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-76cc2766f4418e88125a1735cbe31ff4_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-76cc2766f4418e88125a1735cbe31ff4_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"gPVlm1L2\">根本不是艾宾浩斯提出来的。目前可以追溯到的，最早的，体现多次复习对遗忘曲线影响的图表，是 Paul Pimsleur 在 1967 年的论文 A Memory Schedule 中提出的：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-492cb3201460f2a7a9a1569f0a363661_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"375\" data-original-token=\"v2-492cb3201460f2a7a9a1569f0a363661\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e377758cb546c8bfa64afb7a6dbb6459_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-492cb3201460f2a7a9a1569f0a363661_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;375&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"375\" data-original-token=\"v2-492cb3201460f2a7a9a1569f0a363661\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e377758cb546c8bfa64afb7a6dbb6459_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-492cb3201460f2a7a9a1569f0a363661_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-492cb3201460f2a7a9a1569f0a363661_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/><figcaption>https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1540-4781.1967.tb06700.x</figcaption></figure><p data-pid=\"KU5_DeWE\">另外，这幅图中也不存在所谓的牢记现象：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ee48730bace03bd104861b0d1ae5c2df_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"722\" data-rawheight=\"460\" data-original-token=\"v2-ee48730bace03bd104861b0d1ae5c2df\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d2f2054cb9e550235082d91f918e9d1c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"722\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-ee48730bace03bd104861b0d1ae5c2df_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;722&#39; height=&#39;460&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"722\" data-rawheight=\"460\" data-original-token=\"v2-ee48730bace03bd104861b0d1ae5c2df\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d2f2054cb9e550235082d91f918e9d1c_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"722\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-ee48730bace03bd104861b0d1ae5c2df_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ee48730bace03bd104861b0d1ae5c2df_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"ElkGLhE5\">在这张图中，遗忘曲线变平，似乎暗示了记忆程度将不会随时间下降。但在现实生活中，几乎不存在这种记忆。举个例子，你还记得你小学同学的名字么？能记得几个？很久没联系的那些同学你能想起来吗？</p><p data-pid=\"SYz_vPz2\">然后，题主提到的这种记忆方法，实际上叫做间隔重复（spaced repetition），通过合理安排复习间隔多次主动回忆所学内容，可以巩固记忆，减缓遗忘，但并不意味着能够让你永远记住。</p><p data-pid=\"3xcyOYTy\">关于间隔重复是否有效，有很多文献通过对照实验证明：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/420924493\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c411e5e812bd614048b34e5a1f48eb9f_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"2240\" data-image-height=\"1264\" class=\"internal\">叶峻峣：(3/5) 高效学习的间隔重复——文献综述之间隔效应</a><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c932be024fef955f93dd30e9fa701352_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"757\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-c932be024fef955f93dd30e9fa701352\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f5680cadce4d3500c419a1da9f98e581_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"757\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c932be024fef955f93dd30e9fa701352_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;757&#39; height=&#39;608&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"757\" data-rawheight=\"608\" data-original-token=\"v2-c932be024fef955f93dd30e9fa701352\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f5680cadce4d3500c419a1da9f98e581_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"757\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c932be024fef955f93dd30e9fa701352_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c932be024fef955f93dd30e9fa701352_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"Nuw9n3YQ\">希望能解答题主的疑惑。</p><p data-pid=\"34x63i17\"><br/>本文已加入：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/collection/925510885\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">艾宾浩斯记忆法打假合集</a><p></p>",
